data.description: Seller is offer $10,000 in assistance in the maintenance of the pool. New roof as of January 2022 Water softener added by SJ Johnson  Appliances all upgraded stainless steel Floors in living space updated.  Nestled in the heart of Southern Maryland, this charming home offers the epitome of convenience and comfort with not one but two primary bedrooms—one on the main floor and another on the second floor. Designed with flexibility in mind, this unique feature caters to various lifestyle preferences, providing you with options for both accessibility and elevated views.  The outdoor space of this enchanting home is where the magic truly begins, inviting you to embrace a lifestyle of leisure and entertainment. Picture yourself hosting lively weekend barbecues for friends and family. With plenty of space for grilling, outdoor seating, and recreational activities, this property transforms into a dynamic entertainment hub. Create lasting memories against the backdrop of your own outdoor haven. For those with a green thumb, the possibilities are endless. Transform portions of the vast landscape into a garden oasis where vibrant flowers, aromatic herbs, and lush greenery flourish. Cultivate your own slice of paradise, right in your backyard, and revel in the joy of nature's beauty just steps away from your door.   This home is not just a residence; it's a lifestyle. From the dual primary bedrooms for added convenience to the outdoor space that beckons you to connect with nature, every aspect of this property has been thoughtfully designed for those who appreciate the finer things in life. Schedule a showing and make this Southern Maryland gem your forever home.
